  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a bonus action, you may choose any number of creatures that you can see within 60 feet of you that have commlinks, headcomms, or other such communications devices. Each creature must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or take sonic damage equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of one). Additionally, on a failed save, their communication devices are disabled until rebooted.</p>\n<p>Once you've used this feature, you must complete a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p>",
